headline: Why Elevance Health (ELV) Shares Are Falling Today
summary: Shares of health insurance provider Elevance Health (NYSE:EVH) fell 3% in the afternoon session after the U.S. Commerce Department initiated a national security investigation into medical equipment and devices, raising concerns about potential tariffs.
